{"tid":1331927,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集中討論] Hard mode 中國文宣組","createTime":"2019-07-19T06:21:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T06:23:40.000Z","uid":21678,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6f8424cf2a5f24f5213024f1f368c434ddd32ce0","tid":1331927,"uid":21678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T06:21:40.000Z","msg":"眾所鳩知<br />\n中國防火牆係維穩機器中最重要一環<br />\n因為現今世代<br />\n一個小小的香港火花<br />\n有機會響中國成千上萬的城巿<br />\n燒起熊熊烈火<br />\n<br />\n而推動針對中國國民的文宣<br />\n亦可以正面幫助香港的運動<br />\n包括：<br />\n1. 爭取各省民意支持<br />\n2. 為中共添煩添亂，無法集中處理香港問題<br />\n3. 加重中部維穩駛費<br />\n4. 將香港近年兩場運動的經驗，傳遞給有需要的人<br />\n5. 宣傳去大台 / 不割蓆等等應付中共慣用維穩手法的方法"},{"pid":"aea6242e4195afb43c05240b5769d7b16196a3b9","tid":1331927,"uid":2612,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T06:22:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fGEm7kx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfGEm7kx.png&h=84eef868&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VR1gWdS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVR1gWdS.png&h=e9b1febb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4w4Y9yT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4w4Y9yT.png&h=5088c22f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>有人話我知原來7月20取消左<br />\n<br />\nPrint 出黎痴係連儂牆比老人家知<br />\n<br />\nAirdrop 比人<br />\n<br />\n唔好搞到老人家白行一趟</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06a3d186ee13a03528582ae28dabc86f1c58d1c1","tid":1331927,"uid":21678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T06:22:23.000Z","msg":"而宣傳重點可以有以列幾方面：<br />\n- 解釋香港送中事件始末<br />\n- 警察濫權<br />\n- 香港政府腐敗無能<br />\n<br />\n由於題目太多<br />\n歡迎大家補完"},{"pid":"8470274346693b22adb6f6968cd0ab80878557f6","tid":1331927,"uid":21678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T06:22:44.000Z","msg":"切記千祈唔好激起兩地矛盾<br />\n尤其係「支那、土共、習敗敗」一類嘅字<br />\n儘量唔好講<br />\n因為一講佢地就會起鋼，然後唔肯聽所有嘢"},{"pid":"97b49b841a231432cf2690b292de4e09452e2208","tid":1331927,"uid":21678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T06:23:40.000Z","msg":"搞咁多嘢<br />\n最終目的只有一個<br />\n就係燃點起中國人民對渴望自由、寧死抗爭嘅心<br />\n達到輸出革命、火燒後爛嘅功效<br />\n<br />\n祝　武運昌隆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}